defending the principles of the revolution, saying that "we need
to learn that differences of opinion is not the same as internal
conflict."
</P>
<P>
However, he stressed it was important to observe the law and
to use logic in the debates.
</P>
<P>
Touching the country's economic situation, Khatami said that
increasing production, social security and reforming the country's
tax system are amongst prerequisites for reforming the economic
structure of the country.
</P>
<P>
