justice, progress and a thriving economy," he added.
</P>
<P>
The Iranian Majlis Speaker Ali Akbar Nateq Nouri also
highlighted the importance of harmony between the cabinet and the
Majlis, saying that harmony amongst the three branches of the
country would help frustrate the conspiracies hatched by foreign
powers against the country. 
