Ronaldo has scored six goals this season and helped Inter stay
on top of the Italy's Serie A with a 7-1-0 record.
</P>
<P>
Germans and Italians dominate the Golden Ball list with eight
players. The results of the poll is not expected to be open until
Dec. 23. 
