<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, November 20 (Xinhua) -- A delegation of the
Parliamentary Party of the Pakistan Muslim League (PML) led by
Chief Minister of the North West Frontier Province Mehtab Abbasi
called on President Farooq Leghari here this evening.
</P>
