seedings for the World Cup draw, the world soccer governing body
said on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
In a statement issued on Thursday, FIFA said it may combine a
team's spot in its monthly ranking list with its previous
performance in the World Cup finals to decide which six teams will
join defending champions Brazil and hosts France as seeds.
</P>
<P>
The 1998 World Cup finals draw is scheduled for December 4 in
the Southern French city Marseille.
</P>
<P>
In 1994 World Cup in the United States, countries were seeded
according to a calculation based upon their results in the 1982,
1986 and 1990 World Cup finals. 
