hurdle at the 500,000 U.S. dollars ATP Doubles Championships on
Wednesday at Hartford, the United States.
</P>
<P>
The "Woodies" lost the first two games and came back to defeat
the American team of Don Johnson and Francisco 6-4, 6-1 in just
over one hour.
