seeking for their seven doubles titles this season.
</P>
<P>
Second seeds Jacco Eltingh and Paul Haarhuis of the Netherlands
beat Canada's Daniel Nestor and Mark Knowles of the Bahamas 6-4,
7-6 (7-1).
</P>
<P>
The top two teams from each group advance to the semi-finals
Saturday. 
