<HEADLINE> Investment in 21 Key Projects in Fujian </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, November 20 (Xinhua) -- Fujian Province in southeast
China has invested 5.48 billion yuan (about 682 million U.S.
