1997, a 25.4 percent increase over the same period of 1996.
</P>
<P>
The province will invest 8.56 billion yuan (about 1.07 billion
U.S. dollars) in these projects this year, according to a plan of
the provincial government.
</P>
<P>
These 21 key projects will involve a total investment of 40.97
billion yuan (about 5.12 billion U.S. dollars), according to the
plan.
</P>
<P>
