capacity of 5 million tons of cement a year, with a total net
assets of 1.78 billion yuan (about 222 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
Experts said the new cement group will be more competitive in
domestic and overseas markets.
</P>
<P>
Once the group begins operations, its profits are expected to
increase by 100 million yuan (about 12 million US dollars) in
comparison to profits of the original five cement works.
</P>
<P>
The group is expected to produce 800 million tons of cement
annually and gain more than 5 billion yuan (about 625 million
U.S. dollars) in annual sales by the end of 2000, which would rank
first in the country.
</P>
<P>
The group is expected to become the largest cement producer
in the country in 2010.  
</P>
