undertaken by Russia, in contact with all the other members of the
P5 (five permenant members of the U.N. Security Council), which the
participants in the meeting hope will lead to the unconditional
decision by the leadership of Iraq to accept the return of the
personnel of the Special Commission of the U.N. Security Council
