three months if she had kept skating without treatment. The injury
happened in August during a traning session in Lake Arrowhead at
her home facility.
</P>
<P>
The injury was aggravated two weeks ago when Kwan won at Skate
Canada. She fell when pain began as she was attempting a
butterfly spin in the free program, Carroll said.
</P>
