<HEADLINE> Former Legislator Held for Illicit Enrichment </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SANTA FE DE BOGOTA, November 19 (Xinhua) -- Former Colombian
legislator Carlos Alberto Ramirez Hoyos was arrested today and
charged with illicitly enriching himself.
</P>
<P>
He was to go before an inquiry at the Regional Prosecutor's
office in Santa Fe de Bogota, and would be released afterwards,
said Security Department sources.
</P>
<P>
Carlos Ramirez was among those denounced for having received
money from the Cali drug cartel during the last legislative
elections in 1994. 
