<P>
PARIS -- France said Wednesday that it is ready to fill out its
presence in the United Nations special commission on arms
inspection in Iraq (UNSCOM), if it is asked to provide
supplementary personnel in the mission.
</P>
<P>
"It is up to the special commission on disarmament of Iraq to
analyze the situation. If it asks us to do more, we will examine
