<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, November 19 (Xinhua) -- Six F-117a stealth fighters
landed at Langley Air Force Base in Virginia today on their way
from their base in New Mexico to Kuwait to join the U.S. air and
naval force already in the Gulf for possible military action on
